# 🚀 Personal Portfolio

A modern, responsive **Portfolio Website** built using **React.js** and **TailwindCSS**.  
It highlights my **skills**, **projects**, and provides ways to **connect** with me.

---

## 📄 Features

- 🔹 Fully responsive design (Mobile / Tablet / Desktop)
- 🔹 Component-based architecture with **React**
- 🔹 Clean and fast UI using **TailwindCSS**
- 🔹 Smooth animations using **Framer Motion**
- 🔹 Showcases **Projects**, **Skills**, and **Contact Links**
- 🔹 Easy to maintain and extend

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- ⚛️ **React.js**
- 🎨 **TailwindCSS**
- 🎞️ **Framer Motion** (for animations)
- 🔗 **React Icons** (for social/media icons)

